source/Cambodia\", \"score\": 0.6197895175395706, \"rank\": 0.5681335071767287, \"text\": \"Cambodian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambodia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambodia\"}, {\"begin\": 2021, \"end\": 2026, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999977263, \"rank\": 2.2927001727544355e-12, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"With her phone in hand, she captured the electrifying moment when VannDa took to the stage.\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2201, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The closing ceremony of the 2024 Paris Olympics at Stade De France on August 11.\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2283, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"PHOTO: SUPPLIED/THE PHNOM PENH POST  Below her video, she wrote, \\\"Omgggg, VannDa is performing at the Paris 2024 Olympics Closing Ceremony.\", \"from\": 2284, \"to\": 2423, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am really proud to hear a Cambodian song on this stage!\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2481, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2452, \"end\": 2461, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambodia\", \"score\": 0.6197895175395706, \"rank\": 0.5681335071767287, \"text\": \"Cambodian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambodia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambodia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Among all the 206 countries participating in the 2024 Olympics, Cambodia is here to perform in this spectacular event.\", \"from\": 2482, \"to\": 2600, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2546, \"end\": 2554, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambodia\", \"score\": 0.9999990211956872, \"rank\": 9.687871566139193e-07, \"text\": \"Cambodia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambodia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cambodia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \